#!new # vim:syntax=sh:tw=72

# REQUIREMENTS & DEFAULTS
#-require CXX=[a-zA-Z].*
#-require CC=[a-zA-Z].*
#-require TOOLDIR=/[a-zA-Z].*

# BRIEF
#! Creates cmake toolchain file

=pod

=head1 NAME

B<toolchain template> - Creates a simple cmake toolchain file

=head1 SYNOPSIS

B<new> toolchain I<OPTIONS> NAME TOOLDIR=PATH CXX=PATH CC=PATH

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Creates a basic toolchain file for cmake.

=head1 PARAMETERS

=over

=item CC        
=item CXX       
=item MAJOR     
=item MINOR     
=item PROCESSOR 
=item SYSTEM    
=item TOOLDIR   
=item VENDOR    
=item VERSION   

=back

=head1 REQUIREMENTS

An appropriate version of cmake.

